Package edu.umn.nlpie.mtap.processing

Annotation Type PropertyDescription

@Documented
@Target(TYPE)
@Retention(RUNTIME)
public @interface PropertyDescription
A description of the properties of labels.

  • Required Element Summary

    Required Elements 
    Modifier and Type Required Element Description
    java.lang.String name
    The name of the property.

  • Optional Element Summary

    Optional Elements 
    Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
    java.lang.String dataType
    The data type of the property: str, float, or boolean; List[T] or Mapping[T1, T2] of those.
    java.lang.String description
    A short description of the property.
    boolean nullable
    Whether the property can have a valid value of null.

  • Element Details

    • name

      java.lang.String name
      The name of the property.
      Returns:
      String accessor name of the property.

    • description

      java.lang.String description
      A short description of the property.
      Returns:
      Description of the property.
      Default:
      ""

    • dataType

      java.lang.String dataType
      The data type of the property: str, float, or boolean; List[T] or Mapping[T1, T2] of those.
      Returns:
      String data type of the property.
      Default:
      ""

    • nullable

      boolean nullable
      Whether the property can have a valid value of null.
      Returns:
      True if null is valid, False if null is not valid.
      Default:
      false
